lead_paragraph: Alexis Peterson had 27 points, six rebounds and five steals to help No. 20 Syracuse beat Michigan State 75-64 in a ACC/Big Ten Challenge game on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Peterson Leads No. 20 Syracuse Over Michigan State
